{{#base headerTitle="Client Portal Password Reset" headerSubtitle="Reset your client portal password securely"}}

<div class="greeting">
    Hello {{clientName}}!
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p>🔒 We received a request to reset the password for your {{appName}} client portal account. If you requested this change, you can set a new password by clicking the secure link below.</p>
    
    <p>For your security, this password reset link will expire in <strong>1 hour</strong> and can only be used once.</p>
</div>

<div class="cta-section">
    <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="cta-button">Reset Password</a>
</div>

<div class="warning-notice">
    <p>⚠️ <strong>Important Security Notice:</strong> If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email. Your client account remains secure.</p>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>🛡️ Account Security Details</h4>
    <div class="detail-grid">
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Client Account</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{clientEmail}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Request Time</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{requestTimestamp}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">IP Address</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{ipAddress}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Link Expires</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{expiryTime}}</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p><strong>Having trouble with the button?</strong> Copy and paste this secure link into your browser:</p>
    <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #A855F7; font-family: monospace; background: #f8fafc; padding: 10px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 10px 0;">{{resetUrl}}</p>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>🏢 Your Client Portal Access</h4>
    <p>Once your password is reset, you'll have access to:</p>
    <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Project Status:</strong> Track progress on your active projects</li>
        <li><strong>Invoices & Billing:</strong> View and download invoices</li>
        <li><strong>Support Tickets:</strong> Submit and track support requests</li>
        <li><strong>Document Library:</strong> Access project files and reports</li>
        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Direct messaging with your account manager</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="error-notice">
    <p>🚨 <strong>Didn't Request This?</strong> If you believe someone else is trying to access your account, please contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600;">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>📞 Need Help?</h4>
    <p>Our client support team is here to assist you:</p>
    <div class="detail-grid">
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Email Support</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{supportEmail}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Phone Support</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{supportPhone}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Office Hours</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Mon-Fri, 8AM-5PM CAT</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p><strong>After resetting your password:</strong></p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 20px; color: #4b5563;">
        <li>You'll be redirected to the client portal sign-in page</li>
        <li>Use your email and new password to access your account</li>
        <li>You'll receive a confirmation email for the password change</li>
        <li>All previous sessions will be automatically terminated</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

<div class="success-notice">
    <p>💚 <strong>We're Here to Help:</strong> If you need assistance with your password reset or accessing your client portal, our support team is available during business hours.</p>
</div>

{{/base}} 